original_title: Heino What You Did Last Summer
overview: Heino has a morning program on the local radio station, but he is completely bored with old listeners and sponsored quizzes. That's why he invented the "Heino what you did last summer" program - and the audience in the hall is the program's listeners.  Co-starring is Palle Birch, double Danish champion in improv comedy (2018 + 2019)
title: Heino What You Did Last Summer
